{"tid":2516022,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"屌，壹傳媒咪又係鳩抄人地呃流量","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:16:33.000Z","uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96caec050c007a5f7d4309bbc622a3854c229905","tid":2516022,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"話說，我啱啱睇到壹週刊有個報道，講盧覓雪評論Mirror。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wgKdbfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwgKdbfj.jpg&h=b320170f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦，俾佢吸引咗入去，原來個訪問佢話係引用其他網媒，唔係佢哋自己做：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYmo5874QdbZdadNpoLPE5hcC14HeJfXiinHGawpdFxYA?filename=GyeXCVS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyeXCVS.jpg&h=914bc886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb4jfzmxnH6vPMYFbz8pQh3nFeSq27xEAvyA991ab5mwa?filename=90FWTug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90FWTug.jpg&h=097931be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我想睇返盧覓雪講乜嘢，上網搵咗一輪，原來條片喺度：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/5gOUuhxuO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F5gOUuhxuO4%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=e0b82de0\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/5gOUuhxuO4/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbsL55SJw4sbxYJHU5AzouYLGzmhFdjNoAyqmbHVWy2FH?filename=nkA0AKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkA0AKu.png&h=ccfcdda1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對比番成個訪問，壹週刊真係由頭到尾都抄晒，搵完一大輪，先知原來佢哋都係偷人嘅。<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得啲人話做媒體咁難生存，好地地做咗個訪問，credit都無，被大台一句唔該偷咗。<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒，毒果都係算9數啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}